{"tid":1561693,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"連仔可唔可以整個求救/自爆功能?","createTime":"2019-09-11T16:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T12:38:03.000Z","uid":4308,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"915cafd48ac74e3c7e72b50b03951cdc0dca2c10","tid":1561693,"uid":4308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:40:18.000Z","msg":"見到好多巴絲都因為自爆或者有敏感留言要求del post或del ac <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但有時要推上熱門一排連仔/望遠先望到做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推左上熱門班mon post狗/藍屍都已經肯定cap低圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁不如直接整個功能比唔小心嘅巴絲有更快捷同保密嘅方法搵連仔/望遠<br />\n再唔係整多個自爆功能，唔小心打錯野都可以即刻&quot;自爆&quot;個AC<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\naccount資料同過去留言暫時或永久係連登消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然都要諗諗有咩防止濫用方法<br />\n希望可以快捷保護都手足們<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a05be7d1674727acb77083a793d95a49c927059","tid":1561693,"uid":5682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:40:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 遮打見！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div><